    <div>
      <h3>Filling out & Sending reports</h3>
      <p>
        This would be the core feature of the carrier-side app. To best
        accommodate postal workers who are constantly on the go, the report has
        been made to be as short-handed as possible: interactions will be
        primarily through button inputs, and text input prompts will be kept to
        a bare minimum of one field.
